headline: CBRE Announces Expanded $5 Billion Stock Repurchase Authorization
summary: DALLAS, November 21, 2024--CBRE Group, Inc. (NYSE: CBRE) today announced that its Board of Directors has approved an expanded authorization for the repurchase of up to an additional $5 billion of shares.
